      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 text-primary">•</span>
        <span
          >困惑于复杂操作？直观的UI设计人性化交互逻辑，让专业能力轻松上手。</span
        >
      </li>
    </ul>

